rmine\nour sensitivity allowing us to only place upper or lower limits. However a\njoint analysis of these four systems yields a measurement of their average\nlifetime of $\\langle t_{\\rm Q}\\rangle = 1.17^{+1.77}_{-0.84}$ Myr. We discuss\nour short ~1 Myr inferred lifetimes in the context of other quasar lifetime\nconstraints and the growth of SMBHs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Oct 2018 12:09:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-23"}
